### Get all ITEMs
GET https://localhost:8443/items HTTP/1.1


### Get 1 ITEM
GET https://localhost:8443/items/1 HTTP/1.1

### ADD 1 ITEM
POST https://localhost:8443/items HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "newperson",
    "email": "gosia@gmail.com",
    "password": "letters",
    "avatarUrl": "/avatars/Avatar 2.png"
}


### Delete 1 ITEM
DELETE https://localhost:8443/items/5 HTTP/1.1


### Update a 2nd ITEM
PUT https://localhost:8443/items/2 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "avatarUrl": "/avatars/teste.jpeg"
}

### ADD WITH VALIDATION ITEM
POST https://localhost:8443/validateName
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Norikaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa"
}


